e ref="#pmb2121">Schnitzler, Arthur</persName><placeName ref="#pmb30">Salzburg</placeName><date when="1903-01-14" n="01">14. 1. 1903</date></correspAction><correspAction type="received"><persName ref="#pmb10863">Beer-Hofmann, Richard</persName><placeName ref="#pmb173">Rodaun</placeName><date when="1903-01-15">15. 1. 1903</date></correspAction><correspContext><tei:ref type="belongsToCorrespondence" target="#pmb10863">Beer-Hofmann, Richard</tei:ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="1902-12-24_02">Schnitzler an Beer-Hofmann, 24. 12. 1902</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="1903-01-16_01">Schnitzler, Gussmann an Beer-Hofmann, 16. 1. 1903</ref></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc><encodingDesc><refsDecl><ab>References to Arthur Schnitzler’s diary online consist of the relevant dates only, 
